title: Extend “Foundation Bonus” Staking Rewards
body:
⭐️ Context (please read): https://community.iotex.io/t/community-vote-extend-foundation-bonus-staking-rewards/3401

This proposal is to extend the Foundation Bonus for one year starting with the launch of Mainnet v1.5 in Q4 2021. The Foundation Bonus rewards consist of 80 IOTX per epoch for all Top 36 Delegates -- in total, the IoTeX Foundation will provide an additional ~25M IOTX in rewards for Delegates and voters. These additional incentives will incentivize better service/uptime from Delegates, making IoTeX more reliable and decentralized.

- Any IoTeX stakeholder (i.e., those that stake IOTX) can vote
- Voting Period: Wednesday, September 15 - Friday, September 24
- Implementation (if accepted): Mainnet v1.5 (Q4 2021)
